""" Images - iterate through collection multiple times """
images = Images(['files/0_100.jpg', 'files/1_100.jpg', 'files/2_100.jpg',
    'files/0_100g.jpg'], [0, 1, 2, 3])
images.split = 0.5
ref = images._train[:]
for i in range(0, 4):
    data, label = next(images)
    self.assertTrue(label in ref)
    data, label = next(images)
    self.assertTrue(label in ref)
    data, label = next(images)
